1 (iii) a member of the faculty, including a faculty librarian, EXCEPT
2 FOR NONTENURE TRACK FACULTY;
3 (iv) a student employee, including a teaching assistant or a
4 comparable position, fellow, or post doctoral intern;
5 (v) a contingent, contractual, temporary, or emergency employee,
6 EXCEPT FOR NONTENURE TRACK FACULTY;
